graph TD
    A[Start] --> B[Initialize ProductDetectionSystem]
    B --> C[Load YOLO Model]
    B --> D[Initialize OCRProcessor]
    B --> E[Initialize ImprovedProductMatcher]
    
    F[Process Frame] --> G{YOLO Detection}
    G --> H[Detect Objects]
    H --> I[For each detected object]
    I --> J[Extract bounding box]
    J --> K[Get class name]
    K --> L[Match product with ImprovedProductMatcher]
    L --> M[Add to YOLO detections]
    
    F --> N{OCR Detection}
    N --> O[Perform OCR]
    O --> P[For each OCR result]
    P --> Q[Check confidence > threshold]
    Q --> R[Match product with ImprovedProductMatcher]
    R --> S[Add to OCR detections]
    
    M --> T[Combine YOLO and OCR detections]
    S --> T
    
    T --> U[Draw bounding boxes and labels]
    
    V[Get Final Product] --> W[Aggregate detection scores]
    W --> X[Calculate average confidence]
    X --> Y{Confidence > threshold?}
    Y -->|Yes| Z[Return best product]
    Y -->|No| AA[Return 'Low confidence detection']
    
    subgraph ImprovedProductMatcher
        AB[Match Product] --> AC[Vector DB search]
        AC --> AD[Return matched product and confidence]
    end
    
    subgraph OCRProcessor
        AE[Perform OCR] --> AF[Process image]
        AF --> AG[Return text, bounding box, and confidence]
    end
